HEADWORD: Desinent
<hw>Des"i*nent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>desinens</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>desinere</ets>, <ets>desitum</ets>,
to leave off, cease; <ets>de-</ets> + <ets>sinere</ets> to let,
allow.]</ety> <def>Ending; forming an end; lowermost.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧Their <xex>desinent</xex> parts, fish.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>B. Jonson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
